DateTime::Locale::bo(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::bo(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::bo

SYNOPSIS

  use DateTime;
  my $dt = DateTime->now( locale => 'bo' );
  print $dt->month_name();

DESCRIPTION

This is the DateTime locale package for Tibetan.

DATA

This locale inherits from the DateTime::Locale::root locale.

It contains the following data.
